Also, for some reason it seemed to be installing the same driver 4 times for each different driver that needed to be installed/updated. 
On the plus side, the wireless adapter that it installed now allows me to use the Internet, so that works at least. I can't say for sure that I haven't been turned into a botnet in the process, however.
